Randy Boone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Randy_Boone 0 Clyde Randall "Randy" Boone (born January 17, 1942) is an American former actor and country music singer. He is most well known for appearing in recurring episodes of all three 90 minute western television shows that aired during the 1960s: Wagon Train, The Virginian and Cimarron Strip.
